# Deny by default: only files required by the production builds are exposed to
# Docker or remote BuildKit builders. This keeps local configs, signing keys,
# logs, editor state, release artifacts, and unrelated platform builds out of
# the build context.
**

!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock

!assets/
!assets/**

!snapdog/
!snapdog/**
!snapdog-client/
!snapdog-client/**
!snapdog-common/
!snapdog-common/**
!snapdog-testkit/
!snapdog-testkit/**
!xtask/
!xtask/**

!webui/
!webui/**
webui/node_modules/
webui/.next/
webui/out/
webui/coverage/
webui/.env*
webui/*.log
